messages.message:
To increase visibility on this, wanted to post a demo to the new flow dashboard. It has reached feature parity with the old dashboard and added a bunch of new functionality. Please have a look and comment! You can get to this new dashboard at `/apps/flow/dashboard/`
https://www.loom.com/share/5bbda9bb644c41a3a4ad00df73736c1a

any feature requests will get put into jira.
This Flow dashboard work is cool @Eric Han what Jira is this work associated with? Will this new dashboard be in the July release?
Wooo this is so cool! Looks great!

@Barrie yes it should be in the July release if it satisfies all of our use cases. This is the current task: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/FLOW-571

We may need to make another one to replace the old dashboard with this one.
